title: Emergency Nurses: A&E Stories
overview: Emergency Nurses: A&E Stories throws the spotlight on the incredible work & relatable home lives of some of the NHS's 60,000 most vital staff – nurses on the frontline of A&E. For this second series, we take up residency at Norfolk & Norwich University Hospital, East Anglia's busiest Emergency Department, whose nurses take us behind the curtain of life on AND off the ward.Hard work, true grit & a lot of laughs, these are determined young people who dive-in & thrive in a workplace most of us hope we never have to go to.
